    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "•\nDubli\nCOPENHAGEN\nAmsterdam\nondon\nA Hamburg\nBERLIN\nA Frankfus\nA Paris\nStuttgar\nMunich\nBE\nPLIN GERMAN!",
      "Have Coffee With The Danish\nAnd Toast The Delights Of Berlin.\nNow you can savor the European flavor of\ntwo new choice destinations-Copenhagen and\nBerlin. On May 30, Delta is introducing new\nservice from Atlanta to Copenhagen with a\nstop in London. Our new flight to Berlin, with\na stop in Hamburg, begins on May 2.\nDelta has 9 other destinations in Europe,\nincluding 5 in the united Germany:\nAmsterdam • Dublin • Frankfurt • Hamburg\nLondon • Munich • Paris • Shannon\nStuttgart\nA DELTA\nWe Love To Fly And It Shous®"
    ],
